# Test Roadmap

## Authentication Tests
- Test for successful login with valid credentials. (src/tests/authentication.spec.ts)
- Test for failed login with invalid credentials. (src/tests/authentication.spec.ts)
- Test for token refresh functionality. (src/tests/authentication.spec.ts)

## User Profile Tests
- Test for retrieving user profile. (src/tests/user-profile.spec.ts)
- Test for updating user profile. (src/tests/user-profile.spec.ts)
- Test for handling unauthorized access to profile. (src/tests/user-profile.spec.ts)

## Message Handling Tests
- Test for sending a new message. (src/tests/message-handling.spec.ts)
- Test for retrieving messages in a chat. (src/tests/message-handling.spec.ts)
- Test for marking messages as read. (src/tests/message-handling.spec.ts)
- Test for marking messages as delivered. (src/tests/message-handling.spec.ts)

## Chat Management Tests
- Test for creating a new chat. (src/tests/chat-management.spec.ts)
- Test for retrieving chat details. (src/tests/chat-management.spec.ts)
- Test for retrieving chat list. (src/tests/chat-management.spec.ts)

## Contact Management Tests
- Test for adding a new contact. (src/tests/contact-management.spec.ts)
- Test for updating a contact. (src/tests/contact-management.spec.ts)
- Test for deleting a contact. (src/tests/contact-management.spec.ts)
- Test for retrieving contact list. (src/tests/contact-management.spec.ts)

## WebSocket Tests
- Test for establishing WebSocket connection. (src/tests/websocket.spec.ts)
- Test for sending and receiving messages via WebSocket. (src/tests/websocket.spec.ts)
- Test for handling WebSocket disconnections. (src/tests/websocket.spec.ts)

## Push Notification Tests
- Test for storing device token. (src/tests/push-notification.spec.ts)
- Test for sending push notifications. (src/tests/push-notification.spec.ts)

## File Handling Tests
- Test for uploading a file. (src/tests/file-handling.spec.ts)
- Test for retrieving a file. (src/tests/file-handling.spec.ts)

## Error Handling Tests
- Test for handling 404 errors. (src/tests/error-handling.spec.ts)
- Test for handling 500 errors. (src/tests/error-handling.spec.ts)

## Durable Object Tests
- Test for creating and interacting with Durable Objects. (src/tests/durable-object.spec.ts)
- Test for handling Durable Object alarms. (src/tests/durable-object.spec.ts)
